metadata.name: Cat Herder
metadata.description:
As he watched under a strange sky, he realized the stars he had never seen before, the ones hidden in the darkness.
Who knows what secrets are the tears that wet the ground. How exciting, the mystery to be solved, the riddle is hidden before your eyes.
“I am the helplessness of my greatest fears. I am the true ruler of the hated land. I am a merchant of merchants. I am the most known and the most forgotten.
I am the one who will always be misremembered.”
I'm Cat herder! Cats don't care!..
